      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MUSTANG ETHICS (1) is better than last start when fourth (29.62) from Box 6 at Bulli over 515m. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from seven starts. Can atone. BLAZIN' FIRE (3) spotted a start but wound up strongly late and finished third and beaten 4.5 lengths (25.23) at Maitland in Grade 3/4. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Expecting another good run. SCREAMING VIOLET (6) was out of character last run when missing the frame, finishing seventh (30.09) in a NG at Richmond. Normally fast to begin but shuffled back last time. Has a good record here at this journey. Worth following up. MY MONROE (8) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance – sure to have admirers.",
